; Tests for query.cc: backslash escape handling
; Covers: lines 161-162 (consume_next = true on backslash escape)

2024/01/01 A&B Corp
    Expenses  $10
    Assets

2024/01/02 Other
    Income  $20
    Assets

; Backslash before & prevents it from being treated as AND operator
; and includes it in the identifier (lines 161-162)
; The query '@\&B' means payee matching regex '&B'
test reg '@\&B'
24-Jan-01 A&B Corp              Expenses                        $10          $10
                                Assets                         $-10            0
end test
